{"tid":1165214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登連登分裂絕對啱，因為高登已完全變成支登","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T01:39:09.000Z","uid":201464,"like":34,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"54f77257bed8b37da4eb9172b4afde6c9fdec9a8","tid":1165214,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:39:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7058331&amp;page=1&amp;type=CA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D7058331%26page%3D1%26type%3DCA&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=7d884666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=7058331&amp;page=1&amp;type=CA</a><br />\n部分留言：<br />\n賊登事wfc <br />\n<br />\n派傳單實和平啦<br />\n<br />\n高登仔係焦土派<br />\n拿拿聲通過，俾機會美帝取消關係法<br />\n<br />\n呢類方法有用既話，大劉唔使咁慘啦<br />\n<br />\n連登繼承販民左膠勁做精神<br />\n<br />\n呢個真，仲拖落去對香港有咩好處？<br />\n仲有係香港派傳單無用之餘仲會制造廢紙。<br />\n<br />\n 代大劉多謝連登<br />\n<br />\n關我撚事 <br />\n<br />\n連登仔刺殺淋病我地就支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n派傳單勁做？不了 <br />\n<br />\n權衡利弊嘅今次一定係唔做好過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係支持逃犯條例<br />\n<br />\n唔反販民左膠，香港永冇翻身之日呀<br />\n<br />\n我唔影相點打卡呀, Hi Auntie <br />\n我唔影相點話比人知自己有做野呀 <br />\n我點可以比人誤會自己無出力架 <br />\n我唔影相點樣塑造自己個形象呀 <br />\n我無女食係咪你負責呀 <br />\n我&gt;條條例通唔通過 <br />\n<br />\n係連登仔先咁天真以為做呢啲野仲有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果咁都得佔完中就應該有雙普選啦！<br />\n呢單野過唔過都係睇下中美角力成點，香港人無權話事架啦！<br />\n<br />\n雖然連登唔係好好多，但係通常呢啲留言都係俾人負皮，做唔到主導"},{"pid":"541071d32b9a5124b8d2c1dca9da2c3134662a3e","tid":1165214,"uid":201464,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"<del>五毛</del>三毛快啲負皮咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a329a01b2674226158584eb80d16e90c629a32","tid":1165214,"uid":208726,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73d839dd4cc504bd6578f4259688d057c587c915","tid":1165214,"uid":106326,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"高登多老鬼<br />\n03年見證到依家<br />\n連登99%政治撚00後或留意時事唔夠五年<br />\n大家睇野有分岐好正常"},{"pid":"4b5586d95cf2e642fe50e4f4c681e2c4fe159cf8","tid":1165214,"uid":45285,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73d839dd4cc504bd6578f4259688d057c587c915","tid":1165214,"uid":106326,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"高登多老鬼<br />\n03年見證到依家<br />\n連登99%政治撚00後或留意時事唔夠五年<br />\n大家睇野有分岐好正常"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"所以高登多廢中同私怨撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係識對人唔對事"},{"pid":"9868e148142ff6953ed71b4fcd16f2cf086cdb61","tid":1165214,"uid":106326,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4b5586d95cf2e642fe50e4f4c681e2c4fe159cf8","tid":1165214,"uid":45285,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73d839dd4cc504bd6578f4259688d057c587c915","tid":1165214,"uid":106326,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"高登多老鬼<br />\n03年見證到依家<br />\n連登99%政治撚00後或留意時事唔夠五年<br />\n大家睇野有分岐好正常"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"所以高登多廢中同私怨撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係識對人唔對事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"連登都係偏執<br />\n仲有對人好明顯係有先例<br />\n00後無比人出賣過既感覺係唔會理解<br />\n大家有大家問題<br />\n唔好覺得自己先係岩就得<br />\n衰啲講句如果高登係老屎忽悲觀撚<br />\n連登就係政治幼兒班<br />\n沒有誰比誰高尚"},{"pid":"d92037717754cef09301e086dd98bfef2e4286e0","tid":1165214,"uid":28953,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"其實好少人仲有上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多之前嘅高登巴絲都轉哂用連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl